@hostAddress = http://localhost:5187

### Publish 50 OrderCreated events to Azure Service Bus
POST {{hostAddress}}/events/publish
Accept: application/json

###

### Health check
GET {{hostAddress}}/health
Accept: application/json

###

### OpenAPI spec (JSON)
GET {{hostAddress}}/openapi/v1.json
Accept: application/json

###

### AsyncAPI spec (JSON)
GET {{hostAddress}}/asyncapi/asyncapi.json
Accept: application/json

###

# Scalar UI  -> http://localhost:5187/scalar/v1
# AsyncAPI UI -> http://localhost:5187/asyncapi/ui
